{
  "spec": {
    "title": "Picture-in-Picture",
    "url": "https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "exit Picture-in-Picture algorithm",
      "href": "https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#exit-picture-in-picture-algorithm",
      "html": "When the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"exit-picture-in-picture-algorithm\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">exit Picture-in-Picture algorithm</dfn> is invoked,\nthe user agent MUST run the following steps:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement\">pictureInPictureElement</a></code> is <code>null</code>, throw a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror\">InvalidStateError</a></code> and\nabort these steps.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Run the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#close-window-algorithm\" id=\"ref-for-close-window-algorithm\">close window algorithm</a> with the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-window\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-window①\">Picture-in-Picture\nwindow</a> associated with <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement①\">pictureInPictureElement</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-task\" id=\"ref-for-queue-a-task\">Queue a task</a> to <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire\" id=\"ref-for-concept-event-fire\">fire an event</a> named\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#eventdef-htmlvideoelement-leavepictureinpicture\" id=\"ref-for-eventdef-htmlvideoelement-leavepictureinpicture\">leavepictureinpicture</a></code> using <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#pictureinpictureevent\" id=\"ref-for-pictureinpictureevent\">PictureInPictureEvent</a></code> at the\n<var>video</var> with its <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-event-bubbles\" id=\"ref-for-dom-event-bubbles\">bubbles</a></code> attribute initialized to <code>true</code> and its\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-pictureinpictureevent-pictureinpicturewindow\" id=\"ref-for-dom-pictureinpictureevent-pictureinpicturewindow\">pictureInPictureWindow</a></code> attribute initialized to\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-window\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-window②\">Picture-in-Picture window</a> associated with <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement②\">pictureInPictureElement</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Unset <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement③\">pictureInPictureElement</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Remove one <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-item\" id=\"ref-for-list-item\">item</a> matching <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#relevant-settings-object\" id=\"ref-for-relevant-settings-object\">relevant settings object</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-origin①\">origin</a> from\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#initiators-of-active-picture-in-picture-sessions\" id=\"ref-for-initiators-of-active-picture-in-picture-sessions①\">initiators of active Picture-in-Picture sessions</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "When the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-htmlvideoelement-disablepictureinpicture\" id=\"ref-for-dom-htmlvideoelement-disablepictureinpicture③\">disablePictureInPicture</a></code> attribute is added to a <var>video</var> element,\nthe user agent MAY run these steps:",
      "rationale": "reject",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Reject any pending promises returned by the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-htmlvideoelement-requestpictureinpicture\" id=\"ref-for-dom-htmlvideoelement-requestpictureinpicture\">requestPictureInPicture()</a></code>\nmethod with <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror①\">InvalidStateError</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>video</var> is <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement④\">pictureInPictureElement</a></code>, run the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#exit-picture-in-picture-algorithm\" id=\"ref-for-exit-picture-in-picture-algorithm②\">exit\nPicture-in-Picture algorithm</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "request Picture-in-Picture",
      "href": "https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#request-picture-in-picture",
      "html": "The <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-htmlvideoelement-requestpictureinpicture\" id=\"ref-for-dom-htmlvideoelement-requestpictureinpicture①\">requestPictureInPicture()</a></code> method steps <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-export=\"\" id=\"request-picture-in-picture\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">request Picture-in-Picture</dfn>:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-support\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-support\">Picture-in-Picture support</a> is <code>false</code>, return <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-a-promise-rejected-with\">a promise rejected with</a> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notsupportederror\" id=\"ref-for-notsupportederror\">NotSupportedError</a></code> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>doc</var> be <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-node-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-node-document\">node document</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>doc</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/iframe-embed-object.html#allowed-to-use\" id=\"ref-for-allowed-to-use\">allowed to use</a> the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/permissions-policy-1/#policy-controlled-feature\" id=\"ref-for-policy-controlled-feature\">policy-controlled feature</a>\nnamed <code>\"picture-in-picture\"</code>, return <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-a-promise-rejected-with①\">a promise rejected with</a> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-notallowederror\">NotAllowedError</a></code> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException①\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①\">this</a>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#dom-media-readystate\" id=\"ref-for-dom-media-readystate\">readyState</a></code> attribute is <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#dom-media-have_nothing\" id=\"ref-for-dom-media-have_nothing\">HAVE_NOTHING</a></code>, return <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-a-promise-rejected-with②\">a promise rejected with</a> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror②\">InvalidStateError</a></code> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException②\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this②\">this</a> has no video track, return <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-a-promise-rejected-with③\">a promise rejected with</a> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror③\">InvalidStateError</a></code> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException③\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this③\">this</a>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-htmlvideoelement-disablepictureinpicture\" id=\"ref-for-dom-htmlvideoelement-disablepictureinpicture④\">disablePictureInPicture</a></code> is true, user agent may return <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-a-promise-rejected-with④\">a promise rejected with</a> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror④\">InvalidStateError</a></code> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException④\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>doc</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-element\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-element①\">Picture-in-Picture element</a> is <code>null</code>:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this④\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global①\">relevant global object</a> does not have a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#transient-activation\" id=\"ref-for-transient-activation\">transient activation</a>, then return <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-rejected-with\" id=\"ref-for-a-promise-rejected-with⑤\">a promise rejected with</a> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-notallowederror①\">NotAllowedError</a></code> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException⑤\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#consume-user-activation\" id=\"ref-for-consume-user-activation\">Consume user activation</a> given <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑤\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global②\">relevant global object</a>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑥\">this</a> is <var>doc</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-element\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-element②\">Picture-in-Picture element</a>:",
          "rationale": "return",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Return <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-promise-resolved-with\" id=\"ref-for-a-promise-resolved-with\">a promise resolved with</a> the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-window\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-window③\">Picture-in-Picture window</a> associated with <var>doc</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-element\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-element③\">Picture-in-Picture element</a>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>global</var> be <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑦\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global③\">relevant global object</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>p</var> be <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-new-promise\" id=\"ref-for-a-new-promise\">a new promise</a> created in <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑧\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-realm\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-realm\">relevant realm</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "Return <var>p</var>, and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#enqueue-the-following-steps\" id=\"ref-for-enqueue-the-following-steps\">enqueue the following steps</a> to <var>doc</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-parallel-queue\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-parallel-queue\">picture-in-picture parallel queue</a>:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑨\">this</a> is <var>doc</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-element\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-element④\">Picture-in-Picture element</a>:",
              "rationale": "queue",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-global-task\" id=\"ref-for-queue-a-global-task\">Queue a global task</a> on the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#media-element-event-task-source\" id=\"ref-for-media-element-event-task-source\">media element event task source</a> given <var>global</var> to\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#resolve\" id=\"ref-for-resolve\">resolve</a> <var>p</var> with the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-window\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-window④\">Picture-in-Picture window</a> associated with\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①⓪\">this</a>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p>Abort these steps.</p>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Attempt to associate a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-window\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-window⑤\">Picture-in-Picture window</a> with <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①①\">this</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "If the previous step failed:",
              "rationale": "queue",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-global-task\" id=\"ref-for-queue-a-global-task①\">Queue a global task</a> on the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#media-element-event-task-source\" id=\"ref-for-media-element-event-task-source①\">media element event task source</a> given <var>global</var> to\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#reject\" id=\"ref-for-reject\">reject</a> <var>p</var> with <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror⑤\">InvalidStateError</a></code> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException⑥\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p>Abort these steps.</p>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>pipWindow</var> be a new instance of <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#pictureinpicturewindow\" id=\"ref-for-pictureinpicturewindow①\">PictureInPictureWindow</a></code> that represents <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①②\">this</a>’s associated <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-window\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-window⑥\">Picture-in-Picture window</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-global-task\" id=\"ref-for-queue-a-global-task②\">Queue a global task</a> on the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#media-element-event-task-source\" id=\"ref-for-media-element-event-task-source②\">media element event task source</a> given <var>global</var>, to perform\nthe following steps:",
              "rationale": "if",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p>If <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement⑥\">pictureInPictureElement</a></code> is not <code>null</code>, run the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#exit-picture-in-picture-algorithm\" id=\"ref-for-exit-picture-in-picture-algorithm④\">exit Picture-in-Picture algorithm</a>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p>Set <var>doc</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-element\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-element⑤\">Picture-in-Picture element</a> to <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①③\">this</a>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-append\" id=\"ref-for-list-append\">Append</a> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#relevant-settings-object\" id=\"ref-for-relevant-settings-object①\">relevant settings object</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-origin②\">origin</a> to <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#initiators-of-active-picture-in-picture-sessions\" id=\"ref-for-initiators-of-active-picture-in-picture-sessions②\">initiators of active Picture-in-Picture sessions</a>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①④\">this</a> is <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fullscreen.spec.whatwg.org#dom-document-fullscreenelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-document-fullscreenelement\">fullscreenElement</a>, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fullscreen.spec.whatwg.org#fully-exit-fullscreen\" id=\"ref-for-fully-exit-fullscreen\">exit fullscreen</a>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire\" id=\"ref-for-concept-event-fire①\">Fire an event</a> named <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#eventdef-htmlvideoelement-enterpictureinpicture\" id=\"ref-for-eventdef-htmlvideoelement-enterpictureinpicture\">enterpictureinpicture</a></code> using <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#pictureinpictureevent\" id=\"ref-for-pictureinpictureevent①\">PictureInPictureEvent</a></code> at\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①⑤\">this</a> with its <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-event-bubbles\" id=\"ref-for-dom-event-bubbles①\">bubbles</a></code> attribute initialized to <code>true</code> and its\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-pictureinpictureevent-pictureinpicturewindow\" id=\"ref-for-dom-pictureinpictureevent-pictureinpicturewindow①\">pictureInPictureWindow</a></code> attribute initialized to\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-window\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-window⑦\">Picture-in-Picture window</a>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#resolve\" id=\"ref-for-resolve①\">Resolve</a> <var>p</var> with <var>pipWindow</var>.</p>"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "The <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-document-exitpictureinpicture\" id=\"ref-for-dom-document-exitpictureinpicture\">exitPictureInPicture()</a></code> method, when invoked, MUST\nreturn <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#a-new-promise\" id=\"ref-for-a-new-promise①\">a new promise</a> <var>promise</var> and run the following steps <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#in-parallel\" id=\"ref-for-in-parallel\">in\nparallel</a>:",
      "rationale": "run",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Run the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#exit-picture-in-picture-algorithm\" id=\"ref-for-exit-picture-in-picture-algorithm⑤\">exit Picture-in-Picture algorithm</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If the previous step threw an exception, reject <var>promise</var> with that\nexception and abort these steps.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#resolve\" id=\"ref-for-resolve②\">Resolve</a> <var>promise</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "The <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-documentorshadowroot-pictureinpictureelement⑦\">pictureInPictureElement</a></code> attribute’s getter must run these steps:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①⑦\">this</a> is a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-shadow-root\" id=\"ref-for-concept-shadow-root\">shadow root</a> and its <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-documentfragment-host\" id=\"ref-for-concept-documentfragment-host\">host</a>\nis not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#connected\" id=\"ref-for-connected\">connected</a>, return <code>null</code> and abort these steps.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>candidate</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#retarget\" id=\"ref-for-retarget\">retargeting</a> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/picture-in-picture/#picture-in-picture-element\" id=\"ref-for-picture-in-picture-element⑥\">Picture-in-Picture element</a> against <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①⑧\">this</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>candidate</var> and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①⑨\">this</a> are in the same <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-tree\" id=\"ref-for-concept-tree\">tree</a>,\nreturn <var>candidate</var> and abort these steps.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <code>null</code>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}